This is so very true =)

I feel a Kabong comin on, but wtf -

An in-game friend of mine has a fem high elf pally. I never inquired as to
gender, but I figured it out when she one time said something about her wife
coming home. Many people flirt with her/him and I find it pretty funny, but
never say anything..

You shoulda seen the reactions (s)he incited when she said during a lull in
fighting, "AFK a sec, need to take a dump."

WHOA, too much info! Ack!
It injected a disturbing image of a female highelf into my mind that I don't
care to remember ...
